import { useEffect, useRef, useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import Sidebar from "../components/sidebar"; export default function Admin() { const [researchTitle, setTitle] = useState(""); const [researchYear, setYear] = useState(""); const [category, setCategory] = useState(""); const [file, setFile] = useState(""); const inputRef = useRef(null); const submitFile= async(e) => { e.preventDefault(); const formData = new FormData(); formData.append("Title", researchTitle); formData.append("Year", researchYear); formData.append("Category", category); formData.append("File", file); console.log(researchTitle, researchYear, category, file); const uploadAPI = await axios.post("http://localhost:8081/upload-pdf", formData, { headers: { "Content-type" : "multipart/form-data", }, }); alert(uploadAPI.data.status); setTitle(""); setYear(""); setCategory(""); inputRef.current.value = null; } return( <>
setTitle(e.target.value)} value={researchTitle}/>
setYear(e.target.value)} value={researchYear}/>
Category
setCategory(e.target.value)} >

setFile(e.target.files[0])} />
) }
